title: SeoulFood
typeOfFood: Ovo, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Korean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small place opened 2014 specializing in Korean bibimbap bowls. Also offers salads and sides. Reported 3 of the 8 main dishes are vegan suitable, including a Japche. Mains come with soup and side dish. Order at the counter.
